## 5. Scalability Plan

### 5.1 Short-term (3 months)

- **Problem:** LLM calls are slow (2-5s per call)
- **Solution:** Batch API (Anthropic supports up to 100 requests/batch)

### 5.2 Medium-term (6 months)

- **Problem:** ChromaDB struggles with 100k+ vectors
- **Solution:** Migrate to Milvus or Weaviate (distributed vector DB)

### 5.3 Long-term (12 months)

- **Problem:** API costs too high for daily use
- **Solution:** Fine-tune open-source model (Mistral 7B) on 
  chemistry corpus (generated by Claude)

---

## 6. Security & Privacy

### 6.1 Data Storage

- **Local only:** All uploaded PDFs stored locally
- **No cloud:** ChromaDB runs locally
- **API only:** LLM calls go to Anthropic/OpenAI (no data stored by them)

### 6.2 API Key Security

- **.env file:** Never committed to Git
- **User-specific:** Each user has their own API key
- **No logging:** ChemMind does not log API keys

